OL,3,CBank of England cuts interest rates
OL,4,Cfor second time this year
OL,6,FThe Bank of England has cut interest
OL,7,Frates to their lowest level since 2023.
OL,9,FPolicymakers announced on Thursday
OL,10,Fthat interest rates would set at
OL,11,F4.75%, down 0.25 percentage point from
OL,12,F5%.
OL,14,FIt is the second reduction in rates
OL,15,Fthis year and is the first time rates
OL,16,Fhave been below 5% since June 2023.
