OL,3,CBank of England cuts interest rates
OL,4,Cfor second time this year
OL,6,FReacting to the announcement,
OL,7,FChancellor of the Exchequer, Rachel
OL,8,FReeves, said: "Today's interest rate
OL,9,Fcut will be welcome news for millions
OL,10,Fof families, but I am under no
OL,11,Fillusion about the scale of the
OL,12,Fchallenge facing households after the
OL,13,Fprevious Government's mini-budget.
OL,15,F"This Government's first Budget has
OL,16,Fset out how we are taking the long-
OL,17,Fterm decisions to fix the foundations
OL,18,Fto deliver change by investing in the
OL,19,FNHS and rebuilding Britain, while
OL,20,Fensuring working people don't face
OL,21,Fhigher taxes in their payslips."
