OL,3,CBank of England cuts interest rates
OL,4,Cfor second time this year
OL,6,FExperts said inflation falling below
OL,7,Fthe Bank's 2% target level has
OL,8,Fencouraged policymakers to ease
OL,9,Finterest rates, releasing some more
OL,10,Fpressure on borrowers and mortgage
OL,11,Fholders across the UK.
