OL,3,CBank of England cuts interest rates
OL,4,Cfor second time this year
OL,6,FSome economists said Mr Trump's
OL,7,Feconomic policies, including proposed
OL,8,Ftax cuts and higher trade tariffs, are
OL,9,Finflationary.
OL,11,FThis could prompt policymakers to keep
OL,12,Finterest rates higher for longer, with
OL,13,Fknock-on implications for monetary
OL,14,Fpolicy in the UK.
OL,16,FThe US Federal Reserve will also
OL,17,Fannounce the nation's interest rate on
OL,18,FThursday, with financial markets also
OL,19,Fbetting on a 0.25 percentage point
OL,20,Freduction.
